\section{Conclusion and Future Work}
DDTV introduces an innovative approach to DHCP security using cryptographic challenge-response authentication. Unlike existing solutions, DDTV is proactive, lightweight, and scalable. Future research will explore optimizing performance, integrating with modern security frameworks, and enhancing deployment in cloud environments.

